# MCP Ecosystem Protocol — mcp-sql-rust

OMNI ritual: [`omni-agent-protocol.mdc`](omni-agent-protocol.mdc). Detail: `docs/OMNI_CURSOR_SETUP.md`.

## Decision tree

| Trigger | Tool |
|---------|------|
| Structural / "who calls X?" / impact | **`codegraph_explore`** (required first for `src/**`) |
| Symbol by name | `codegraph_search` / CLI `codegraph query` |
| String literal / config | Shell `rg` / `omni_search` |
| Before edit hot file | `omni_context` or `codegraph_node` |
| Every coding session | `user-omni` session status |
| Large multi-file refactor | plan first (sequential thinking if available) |

## Forbidden

- Native **Grep** tool — use `omni_search` or Shell `rg`
- Dumping entire `src/` files when CodeGraph can answer
- Skipping AST guard when changing execute paths
- Logging secrets from `.env`

## CodeGraph

```bash
codegraph init          # once per clone
codegraph sync          # after large edits
codegraph status
codegraph explore "execute_sql"
codegraph callers validate_and_prepare
```

Index lives in `.codegraph/` (gitignored). WSL: keep index on Linux FS only.
